experiences.description:
- Head of non-agency residential mortgage-backed securities (RMBS) and asset-backed securities (ABS) trading,responsible for managing a $2.5bn proprietary trading book and a $1.5bn liquidity book

- Adopt a fundamentally driven security selection framework with emphasis on downside P&L management via active portfolio construction and diversification

- Managed a trading team of 7 on distressed securitized products and generate/execute proprietary trade ideas

- Led the development of an integrated analytics and risk management platform that incorporated 
(i) loan level data across third-party providers; 
(ii) fundamental bond model analytics/cash flow engine; 
(iii) projecting resulting macro/micro scenario exposures at a portfolio level; 
(iv) automated performance updates and monitoring
